  + [glyphic_enclosure] maps_to confinement or gauge-invariant bound states as a possible physical intuition
  + [symbolic_encryption] maps_to inaccessible nonperturbative structure or gauge-invariant sector, not proof
  + [phase_key] maps_to gauge choice, invariant observable, or constructive method, depending on formalization
  + [mass_gap] maps_to spectral gap above the vacuum in the quantum theory

